The paper is structured as follows. We introduce the notation and the surface operators and explain the integration of the constraint into the full surface Navier–Stokes equations in Section 2. In Section 3, we explain an approach for area conservative surface movement with mesh regularization and discretization of the model by surface finite elements . Based on this, we show numerical convergence studies and simulation results in Section 4. In Section 5, we draw conclusions.
